{"tid":2119194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良促即時禁止全日堂食及強制公共地方戴口罩","createTime":"2020-07-22T03:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T03:46:35.000Z","uid":166360,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"311df29f730e6c16ce3652d047fd6c716d931b1c","tid":2119194,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"何栢良促即時禁止全日堂食及強制公共地方戴口罩<br />\n2020-07-22 HKT 10:53<br />\n<br />\n&quot;港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良表示，現時疫情嚴峻，政府應即時收緊防疫措施，包括全日禁止堂食和強制公共地方要戴口罩，不應再以「擠牙膏」方式處理。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;他認為，當局應針對有病徵的密切接觸者做檢測，不應盲目浪費資源...&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;何栢良接受另一電台節目訪問時指出，如果強制市民在公共場所戴口罩，<span class=\"red\">部分人士應可獲得豁免</span>，例如有讀唇需要人士、兩歲以下小童和<span class=\"red\">進行劇烈運動的人士</span>，但必須有罰則，例如罰款安排，才能有效。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539181-20200722.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539181-20200722.htm&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=ef749daf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539181-20200722.htm&h=56751833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539181-20200722.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">[blue]何生都明白到行山和跑步人士須獲豁免強制戴口罩，但連登恐懼撚唔明[/red]</span></strong>"},{"pid":"12a2c9de22c06c624d7d58da6b5e8e355c371bad","tid":2119194,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"其實「恐懼撚」係咪熱青城發明嘅用語？<br />\n<br />\nBTW大家由呢個post沉。"},{"pid":"3847383bb3b421391746dddcbdd82d324e31030f","tid":2119194,"uid":205043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"係都促全面封關先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g